            <p>领导强调“影响力、可见度、稳定交付”是关键，你有了明确抓手。</p>

<<link "围绕要点行动">>
<<set $performance = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, $performance + (5)))>>
<<set $mental = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, $mental + (2)))>>
<<if !$skills.includes("向上管理")>><<set $skills.push("向上管理")>><</if>>
<<goto "promotion">>
<</link>>


:: improve_process
<h2>流程补强</h2>
            <p>你把事故教训写成检查清单，拉上团队共建防线。</p>

<<link "让团队共建并执行">>
<<set $performance = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, $performance + (4)))>>
<<set $mental = Math.max(0, Math.min(100, $mental + (2)))>>
